        <div n="597-36L-">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-597-36L--headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-597-36L--headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-597-36L--headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="italics">Written in the Year</hi> 1731.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-597-36L--headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-597-36L--headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-597-36L--headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-597-36L--headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-597-36L--headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-597-36L--headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi>POLLO, God of Light and Wit,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-2" n="2">Could Verse inspire, but seldom writ:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-3" n="3">Refin'd all Mettals with his Looks,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-4" n="4">As well as Chymists by their Books:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-5" n="5">As handsome as my Lady's Page;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-6" n="6">Sweet Five and Twenty was his Age.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-7" n="7">His Wig was made of sunny Rays;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-8" n="8">He crown'd his youthful Head with Bays:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-9" n="9">Not all the Court of Heav'n could shew</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-10" n="10">So nice and so compleat a Beau.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-11" n="11">No Heir, upon his Appearance,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-12" n="12">With twenty thousand Pounds a Year Rents,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-13" n="13">E'er drove, before he sold his Land,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-14" n="14">So fine a Coach along the Strand;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-15" n="15">The Spokes, we are by <note place="foot">·──────────<hi rend="italics">Temo aurens, aurea summæ<lb/>Curvatura Rotæ, radiorum argentens ordo</hi>.</note> <hi rend="italics">Ovid</hi> told,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-16" n="16">Were Silver, and the Axel Gold.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-17" n="17">(I own, 'twas but a Coach and Four,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-18" n="18">For <hi rend="italics">Jupiter</hi> allows no more.)</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-19" n="19"><lb/>Yet, with his Beanty, Wealth, and Parts,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-20" n="20">Enough to win ten Thousand Hearts;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-21" n="21">No vulgar Deity above</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-22" n="22">Was so unfortunate in Love.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-23" n="23"><lb/>Three weighty Causes were assign'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-24" n="24">That mov'd the Nymphs to be unkind.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-25" n="25">Nine Muses always waiting round him,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-26" n="26">He left them Virgins as he found 'em.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-27" n="27">His Singing was another Fault;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-28" n="28">For he could reach to <hi rend="italics">B</hi>. in <hi rend="italics">alt</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-29" n="29">And by the Sentiments of <hi rend="italics">Pliny</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-30" n="30">Such Singers are like <note place="foot">·A famous <hi rend="italics">Italian</hi> Singer.</note> <hi rend="italics">Nicolini</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-31" n="31">At last, the Point was fully clear'd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-597-36L--line-32" n="32">In short; <hi rend="italics">Apollo</hi> had no Beard.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
